    "syllabus": {
        "zh": "1. 策略管理與策略性競爭力<br>2. 外部環境分析<br>3. 內部環境分析<br>4. 事業層級策略<br>5. 競爭敵對與競爭動態<br>6. 公司層級策略<br>7. 購併與重整策略<br>8. 國際策略<br>9. 合作策略<br>10. 公司治理<br>11. 組織結構與控制<br>12. 策略領導 <br>13. 策略性創業家精神<br>",
        "en": "1. Strategic Management and Strategic Competitiveness<br>2. The External Environment Analysis<br>3. The Internal Environment Analysis<br>4. Business-Level Strategy<br>5. Competitive Rivalry and Competitive Dynamics<br>6. Corporate-Level Strategy<br>7. Acquisition and Restructuring Strategies<br>8. International Strategy<br>9. Cooperative Strategy<br>10. Corporate Governance<br>11. Organizational Structure and Controls<br>12. Strategic Leadership<br>13. Strategic Entrepreneurship<br>"
